      <section id="id6219194">
        <title>The three little Goats</title>
        <para id="id2713626">One day there were three goats.</para>
        <para id="id8927840">The smallest goat was called Little Billy Goat Gruff.</para>
        <para id="id1167550119406">The middle-sized goat was called Big Billy Goat Gruff.</para>
        <para id="id8502180">The biggest goat was called Great Big Billy Goat Gruff.</para>
        <list id="id8780347" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Draw the three goats.</item>
        </list>
        <figure id="id7461751">
          <media id="id7461751_media" alt="">
