        <para id="id8553573">These three goats lived in a field.</para>
        <para id="id5640272">They ate the fresh green grass.</para>
        <para id="id1167549969492">Near the field was a river.</para>
        <para id="id8933701">There was a bridge over the river.</para>
        <list id="id8731927" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Draw the field, the river and the bridge.</item>
        </list>
