        <para id="id3642705">One day the grass became dry and the goats had nothing to eat. </para>
        <para id="id7136652">Little Billy Goat Gruff said, “See the nice green grass and the red apples on the other side of the bridge. I am going to cross the bridge.” </para>
        <para id="id5787903">“The angry old dwarf will not let you cross the bridge", said Big Billy Goat Gruff. </para>
        <para id="id5483728">“I am not afraid of him," said Little Billy Goat Gruff. </para>
        <para id="id6145213">He ran trip-trap, trip-trap over the bridge.</para>
        <list id="id7143238" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Draw Little Billy Goat Gruff crossing the bridge.</item>
