        <para id="id6266021">The angry old dwarf said, “Who runs trip-trap trip-trap over my bridge?"</para>
        <para id="id8652063">“It is I, Little Billy Goat Gruff.”</para>
        <para id="id6475027">“I am going to eat you!" said the angry old dwarf.</para>
        <para id="id5544861">“No", said Little Billy Goat Gruff, “do not eat me, eat Big Billy Goat Gruff when he comes over your bridge. He is much bigger than me.”</para>
        <para id="id7862807">“Very well", said the dwarf.</para>
        <para id="id5758057">Little Billy Goat Gruff ran over the bridge and ate the nice green grass and the red apples.</para>
